title: Agent@Home Travel Summit: Still Time to Register
text:
Last updated: 11:48 AM ET, Wed September 23 2015 Agent@Home Travel Summit: Still Time to Register Travel Agent | Cruise Lines International Association (CLIA) | Theresa Norton Masek | September 23, 2015 
There’s still time to register for the Agent@Home Travel Summit next week in Atlantic City, N.J., but it’s getting close. 
This is your chance to meet top executives representing some of the travel industry’s leading cruise lines, tour operators, hotel and resort companies, associations and more. Keynote speeches, workshops and panels are specifically targeted to home-based travel agents.
